,Recommended,218640,34061022,Posted: 6 August,all,ｓｕｎｎｙ ｇｉｒｌ,"Today in the gaming industry there are few excellent games in the genre of Horror. But recently there was a game in which you can not only become a victim of evil, but also create it yourself. The history of the game is pretty simple. The boy, who was born on June 6, 1966, lives in a wealthy family, like ordinary children. But when Lucius was six years old, the devil woke up inside him and ordered to kill all his family and servants. In fact, Lucius is Hitman, only about a child with superpowers. A game with an open world, limited by the fence of the mansion. It is interesting that every inhabitant of the mansion can be executed in various ways. Whether it's an accident with the help of mind control, well, or a brutal reprisal in front of everyone. The game is very light for its genre, but does not lose interest. Lucius graphics are excellent. Rough in my opinion looks like an animation. The sound is also not bad. In the end, I want to say that such a game has never existed and will not appear soon."
